    <note>Hu(1) Yixiu [818] Su's [8064] grandson, Lin's [7255] great grandson, Zheng(1) Yong's [8030] son-in-law. He used his grandfather's yin to enter the civil service. His sons all used the same generational indicator in their mingzi as did his mother's brothers. His funerary inscription contains information about a shaman, Zhang Huaisu, who led a rebellion. XCBSB, 20.8a (n.), 16a, 24.1b; SHY:ZG, 68.12a-12b; Li Zhiyi, WJ, 19.119-128. CBD, 2, 1602.</note>
